features: 【WIRELESS CHARGING DESK LAMP】This pink study desk lamp comes with a built-in wireless charging pad, which support max speed of 10W and covers the needs of compatible Qi-enabled supported devices. You can keep your phone charged while you study and never have to worry about running out of power.

【LAMP KEEP DESK ORGANIZED】A dorm room desk lamp with storage is absolutely a must-have item for college. This desk lamp with a pen holder helps to save space as it could storage some small items in it, which make sure the learning desktop always keep organized to avoid losing things and help you more focused.

【3 MODES DIMMING DESK LIGHT】This adjustable LED desk light has three color configurations. Cool white for fun, soft white for the bedroom, and white light for dorm office. Long press to change the office desk lamp's brightness (from 5% to 100%), or short click to switch the color(3000k/4000k/5000k). Additionally, it simply turns on when you reach for the touch power button in the dark.

【EYE CARING LED DESK LAMP】Super bright desk lamps have 56pcs LED beads that can produce 800 lumen of light at a maximum output of 8W of power. They have a lifespan of 50,000 hours and a CRI rate of 90+. Even used for extended periods, an acrylic panel and the gentle non-flickering light helps prevent your eyes from fatigue.

【FLEXIBLE ARM &AESTHETIC ROOM DECOR】The cute gooseneck desk lamp can be bent to 360 degrees arbitrarily, so you could adjust its arm to point the light unit around in any direction as needed. You can even twist into unique shapes to decorate your tabletop or bend it to a small size desk lamp for carrying outside.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Versatile and compact wireless LED desk lamp at exceptional price!!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This LED desk lamp is such a great value! At such an incredible price, I have to say I am quite impressed at its functionality. Well packaged, easy to set up and operate with its sleek and compact design, it fits perfectly with my compact desk area. The penholder offers ample space. I appreciate the three modes of lighting and how easy it is to dim each of them. The wireless charging function is an added bonus. I was skeptical that it would function as advertised, but was pleasantly surprised that my phone immediately started charging when placed in the phone holder area. I couldn’t be more satisfied with this purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing, versatile and practical.
reviews.reviewText: Very warm and bright light!I love this multipurpose table lamp. It has 3 light modes, a wireless phone charger, and a pen holder.It's very bright, but also dimmable to adjust to my needs throughout the day.It's easy to use, sturdy, and a great addition to my bedroom.I highly recommend this item.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very nice and convenient
reviews.reviewText: This is one nice looking and convenient LED lamp.It came in a nice package, well protected. It has a small instructions folding booklet, you never know who may need it even though for most people setting the lamp is very straightforward.There is also a small instructions paper that shows how to set up your phone for charging. Al though not a deal breaker, I would've liked to be able to set up my phone in any direction, especially portrait to be able to use it comfortably while charging.The lamp uses a regular wall connector, it is not USB. The length of the cable is perfect which allows you to set up the lamp around your desk easily without worrying about the cable being too short.The lamp light panel has a nice size. Plus it has three Light modes: warm, normal, and cool white. I tried to take pictures of all three colors but they looked exactly the same :/. Either way, you can see the brightness in the one picture I added.The rubber neck of the lamp feels good on the hand and is very easy to adjust to any direction. The neck is also very sturdy at the same time, this means that it will 100% remain in the position you set it to.Charging the phone was as simple as laying it sideways on the lamp. You would Linley need to remove your phone from the case though.This lamp is just quite convenient while looking modern. Very happy with this purchase.

reviews.reviewTitle: Do I Ever Love This Lamp!!!
reviews.reviewText: I work from my home office in the basement and wanted a desk lamp that would cast a solid white light across the entire work area. Bingo! Since I keep the light positioned on a shelf above my work space, I wanted something that could be turned on and off with a simple touch, without my having to stand up to see/find the switch. Again, Bingo! My cell phone is an aging Pixel 3 that does not hold a charge very well. Even that is no longer a problem, as the built in charger works flawlessly and now my phone is fully charged all day long. Bingo X 2. Love this device and have already purchased a second one for my wife's work space. Highly recommend.
